  "texts": [
    "[29] Our algorithms take three step to generate the ultimate sentences:(1) For the given image (with celebrities appear), we employ a common encoder-decoder architecture for image captioning and generate captions without names.",
    "[30] (2) We use MCTNN and Resnet [34] to get the names of faces appearing in the image.",
    "(3) We parse the output sentence in step(1) and replace the parts with celebrity names accordingly.",
    "Extensive experiments show the feasibility of our method in many simple scenarios.The structure of the report are as follows: Section 2 defines the subtask of our project, which are comprised of Image captioning, Face recognition, Noun phrase(NP) chunks matching.",
    "[51] Section 3 discusses the details of our methods and implementations."
  ],
